{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a4acfa507","title":"给李×的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"417e0cc011","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":17,"articleId":"4a4acfa507"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ba334d0655","type":"paragraph","text":"老百姓拥护共产党，是因为我们代表了民族与人民的要求，但是如果我何不能解决经济间题，如果我们不能建立新式工业，如果我们不能发展生产力，老百姓就-定不拥护我何。","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"061b38fc72","type":"paragraph","text":"如果我们共产党员不关心工业，不关心济，也不得到别的什工有益的工作，对这一些-一无所知，一无所能，只会作一种抽象的“革命工作”，这种重命家是毫无价航的，我们应蔽反对这些尘头革命家，学习使中国工业化的各种技术知。","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"e6f0f836de","type":"paragraph","text":"博引自李先念：《努力学好经济工作》","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"585473f5da","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五二年七月十四日）","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"b6e6fd4ba8","type":"paragraph","text":"封信给、李×的","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"65c700d01a","type":"paragraph","text":"××克：","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"225fb551b9","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十一日的信收到。以前儿也都收到了。爱晚亭三字已照写如另瓶。","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"10e2f6a936","type":"paragraph","text":"矛盾融第四章第十段第三行“无融什么矛盾，也无融在什么时候矛盾着的方面，其发展是不平衡的。”这里“也无在什工时”八字应删，在选集第-卷第二版时，已将这八字去。你写解时，请加注意为盼！","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"1e70d90c4d","type":"paragraph","text":"顺候敬安","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"832ee9a16c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"84225a0950","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年九月十七日视察黄河时的谈话","index":10,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"1d84501f39","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五二年十月二十九日）老根据地的人民出了大力，我何要注意帮助他们。","index":11,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"ac2704e5cd","type":"paragraph","text":"这个大水康（三门峡）修起来，把几千年以来的黄河水患解决啦，还能灌溉平原的农田几千万亩，发电一百万迁，通行输船也有了条件，是可以研究的。","index":12,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"757fd56ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"南方水多，北方水少，如有可能，借一点水来是可以的。","index":13,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"34d372aaf0","type":"paragraph","text":"对民建方针指示的精神","index":14,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"},{"id":"200fbdecf8","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五二年）、私人看本在中国建设上是有查献的，只要不额它向坏的方面发展。","index":15,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507"}],"page":{"id":"0ae32f9505","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"4a4acfa507","start":31,"end":31}}}},"__N_SSG":true}